4-0.query:
SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
 FROM sampled_info_type_1 AS it,
 sampled_keyword_1 AS k,
 sampled_movie_info_idx_1 AS mi_idx,
 sampled_movie_keyword_1 AS mk,
 sampled_title_1 AS t
 WHERE t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
 AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
 AND it.info = '@param0'
 AND k.keyword LIKE '@param1'
 AND mi_idx.info > '@param2'
 AND t.production_year > @param3;
